concept_system_camera => nrel_advantages:
 [1. Small dimensions.](*<- lang_en;; *);
 [2. High image quality. The image quality is the same as that of amateur SLR cameras.](*<- lang_en;; => nrel_using_constants: ... (* <-concept_slr_camera;;*);;*);
 [3. High shooting speed.](*<- lang_en;; *);;
 
